Firayim Ministan Indiya zai halarci bude ginin haikalin a wurin da ake takaddama
NEW DELHI (AP) - Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin bude harsashin ginin wani gidan ibada na Hindu a wani yanki da ake takaddama a arewacin Indiya inda masu tsattsauran ra'ayi na Hindu suka rushe wani masallaci na karni na 16 a shekarar 1992, a cewar hukumar da ke kula da gina haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, ranar da masu shirya taron suka ce ta kasance mai kyau ga 'yan Hindu amma hakan kuma ya nuna shekara guda tun lokacin da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta soke matsayin karamin mulkin mallaka na jihar musulmi daya tilo, Jammu da Kashmir.
Alamar ba ta iya rasawa ga duka magoya baya da abokan adawar Jam'iyyar Bharatiya Janata ta Hindu, ko BJP, wanda a cikin sanarwar ta shekaru da yawa ya haɗa da alkawuran cire ikon cin gashin Kashmir da kuma gina haikalin ga allahn Hindu Ram inda masallacin Mughal ya taɓa tsayawa, wani wuri a cikin birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh wanda masu bautar sun yi imanin cewa wurin haihuwar Ram ne.
Saboda cutar coronavirus har yanzu tana ta yaduwa a duk fadin Indiya, wacce ta bayar da rahoton na uku mafi yawan masu kamuwa da cutar a duniya, za a watsa bikin kai tsaye a gidan talabijin na jihar kuma za a iyakance adadin mahalarta da masu kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko kuma Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, wata kungiyar kishin kasa ta Hindu da ke da alaƙa da BJP.
Haikalin zai zama "cibiyar dawwama da rashin mutuwa ta zaman lafiya, hadin kai da haɗin kai da farkawar jin Hindutva, " ko hanyar rayuwar Hindu, in ji mai magana da yawun kungiyar Vinod Bansal a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Asabar.
An warware takaddama mai tsawon karni a kan wurin a shekarar da ta gabata bayan nasarar da BJP ta samu a zaben.
