Masu zanga-zangar sun fasa tagogi, sun fesa zane-zane, sun harba abubuwan walƙiya kuma sun nuna lasers a kan jami'an, in ji sashen Oakland a shafin Twitter .
Tweets da dama sun yi kira ga zaman lafiya kuma sun nemi masu shirya su "taimake mu samar da wurare masu aminci da wuraren tsaro ga masu zanga-zanga".
