An bayar da umarnin da kasar Sin ta bayar na rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar a Chengdu a ranar Juma'a a matsayin ramuwar gayya ga umarnin Amurka na rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin a Houston, Texas.
