Zanga-zangar Seattle: Wuta da kuma Farin Farin yayin da Dubban Mutane ke Tafiya Ta Cikin Birni
SEATTLE - Bayan makonni na tashin hankali tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Oregon, wani taron mutane kimanin 2,000 sun taru a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna tafiya a tituna suna yin gwagwarmaya da 'yan sanda.
Jami'an 'yan sanda uku sun ji rauni, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar da shi a asibiti da raunin kafa wanda fashewar ta haifar, kuma an kama masu zanga-zanga 16 tun da yamma, in ji 'yan sanda.
Masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya a wurin da za a kafa cibiyar tsare matasa kuma sun kona gine-gine a wurin, suna ɗauke da alamun da suka ce "Feds Go Home" da kuma kururuwa "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya".
Wasu sun fasa tagogin kasuwanni da ke kusa.
'Yan sanda sun fuskanci taron a unguwar Capitol Hill, suna tura bama-bamai da kuma feshin barkono kafin su fara kama mutane.
Bipasha Mukherjee, mai shekara 52, daga Kirkland, Washington, ta ce ta yi zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun watan Mayu kuma ta ce abin damuwa ne a gare ta ganin irin wannan dabarar ta'addanci da 'yan sanda ke yi.
"Wannan ba ƙasar da na ƙaura zuwa ba ce", in ji Ms. Mukherjee, wadda ta zo daga Indiya fiye da shekaru 30 da suka shige.
"Yana jin kamar muna saurin zama wata ƙasa mai fasadi da kuma 'yan sanda".
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce zanga-zangar ta kai hari ne ga hukumomin gari da kuma tura jami'an tarayya wadanda suka yi ta murkushe zanga-zangar da ta dade a Portland.
Mista Savage ya ce dabarun tilasta bin doka a Portland, wanda ya hada da amfani da hayaki da makamai masu hana jama'a, na da hatsari kuma bai dace ba.
"Wannan wani abu ne mai wuya sosai a cikin wani abu mai tsanani", in ji Mr. Savage yayin da yake wanke idanunsa da spray da kuma kula da rauni a hannunsa daga bam din flash.
Mutuwar George Floyd a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a watan Mayu ya haifar da zanga-zangar taro da ta jawo miliyoyin mutane zuwa tituna a birane da dama, amma wadannan zanga-zangar sun ragu a yawancin birane.
Duk da haka, Seattle da Portland sun ga zanga-zanga da suka yi tsawo.
Masu zanga-zangar Seattle a wani lokaci sun yi ikirarin wasu gundumomi na unguwar Capitol Hill kuma sun ayyana yankin cin gashin kai.
Bayan harbe-harbe da aka yi a can ya sa 'yan sanda suka share yankin, zanga-zangar ta ragu.
Portland, a halin yanzu, ta ci gaba da zanga-zanga, tare da wasu daga cikin manyan zanga-zangar a kusa da gine-ginen tarayya a cikin birni.
Bayan da Shugaba Trump ya bayar da umarnin zartarwa don kare mutum-mutumi da dukiyar tarayya, Ma'aikatar Tsaron Cikin Gida ta tura ƙungiyoyin dabaru zuwa garin, ta fara jerin rikice-rikice da suka haifar da raunin masu zanga-zanga, binciken babban jami'in da kuma kira daga shugabannin gida don jami'an tarayya su tafi.
Taron masu zanga-zanga a wannan birni sun ƙaru zuwa dubbai, kuma zanga-zanga a can suna ci gaba.
A wannan makon, jami'an tarayya sun tura wata tawagar da ke Seattle, kuma masu zanga-zanga sun ambaci wannan ci gaba a matsayin daya daga cikin dalilan zanga-zangar ranar Asabar.
Yayin da zanga-zangar Portland ta kasance a cikin gari, zanga-zangar ranar Asabar ta mamaye yankunan da ke gabashin tsakiyar gari, inda kotun tarayya ta birnin take.
