"Rashin nasara" na Amurka na hana neman magungunan coronavirus
Amurka tana hana kokarin duniya na samar da magungunan cutar anti-Covid masu amfani saboda masu bincike suna gwada magunguna a "ta hanyar da ba ta dace ba", in ji masanin da ke jagorantar shirin na Burtaniya.
Shirin gwaji na dawo da cutar na Biritaniya, wanda ya shafi marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitoci da yawa na Biritaniya, ya riga ya gano wani sabon magani mai ban al'ajabi don magance cutar kuma ya nuna wasu biyu - da a baya aka yi zaton za su iya ceton rayuka - a matsayin marasa amfani.
Amma rashin nasarar tsarin likitancin Amurka don daidaita wannan fitowar yana nufin cewa sauran magunguna masu alƙawarin da za a iya yarda da su don amfani da su a ko'ina har yanzu dole ne a kimanta su.
Musamman, plasma mai warkewa (plasma na jini wanda aka karɓa daga marasa lafiyar Covid-19 kuma wanda ke ƙunshe da ƙwayoyin cuta waɗanda zasu iya kare wasu daga cutar) har yanzu ba a gwada shi yadda ya kamata a cikin babban gwaji ba.
"An riga an bai wa dubban mutane jini a Amurka amma ba a yi amfani da wannan magani ba", in ji Farfesa Martin Landray, ɗaya daga cikin waɗanda suka kafa shirin na Warkewa.
"Suna ba mutane jini ne kawai a lokacin da suke warkewa da begen cewa zai yi aiki. An ba da adadi mai yawa kuma har yanzu ba su san ko yana taimaka ko cutarwa ko kuma ba shi da tasiri", in ji Landray, ƙwararre a kafa gwaji na miyagun ƙwayoyi a manyan sikelin.
Amurka ta kasa yin gwaji mai yawa, wanda aka yi a kai a kai kuma hakan ya kawo karshen samar da magunguna marasa kyau.
Gwajin magani na bazuwar shi ne mizanin gwal wajen gano magunguna masu amfani.
Suna kawar da ra'ayin da ba a sani ba da zai iya ɓata ra'ayin likitoci.
Dubban mutane suna shan magani kuma dubban wasu suna shan magani da ake kira placebo.
Ba wanda ya san abin da aka ba su.
Sai a gwada sakamakon kuma a nuna yadda maganin ya yi aiki.
Ta wannan hanyar, Recovery ta iya nuna cewa maganin steroid dexamethasone ya rage mutuwar mutane da kashi ɗaya bisa uku a cikin marasa lafiyar Covid-19 da ke kan na'urar numfashi.
Ya kuma nuna cewa maganin hydroxychloroquine - da ake yawan yin ta - ji - da kuma maganin da aka haɗa da lopinavir da ritonavir - ba su da tasiri wajen ceton rayukan marasa lafiya.
Abu mai mahimmanci waɗannan gwaje-gwajen suna buƙatar adadi mai yawa na marasa lafiya kuma babu wani asibiti guda ɗaya da ya isa don irin wannan binciken.
Biritaniya tana da wata babbar fa'ida - cibiyar kula da lafiyar ƙasa.
Akasin haka, ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya ta Amurka ta rarrabu kuma nasarar ta kawai wajen nuna yiwuwar magani ta kasance tana nuna fa'idar magani mai tsada sosai remdesivir don hanzarta dawo da wasu marasa lafiya na Covid-19.
"Akwai gwaje-gwaje da yawa na ƙananan magunguna da suka shafi fewan dozin ko kuma ɗaruruwan marasa lafiya da ke gudana a Amurka amma babu wani abu mai mahimmanci", in ji Landray.
"Suna kasa yin gwaji masu yawa, da aka yi da son rai kuma hakan ya kawo ƙarshen samar da magunguna marasa kyau. Hakan yana sa aikin magani ya zama mafi muni kuma sakamakon marasa lafiya ya zama mafi muni".
Landray ya ce wannan gazawar ta kasance mai ban haushi musamman idan ya zo ga amfani da plasma mai warkarwa, wanda likitoci da yawa suka yi imanin zai iya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen kula da marasa lafiya masu cutar Covid-19.
