Magajin garin Kansas City ya yi maraba da taimakon gwamnatin tarayya wajen warware kisan kai, amma yana damuwa game da muradin Trump
Magajin garin Kansas City Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi kan dalilin da ya sa Shugaba Trump ya tura jami'an tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimako wajen warware yawan kashe-kashe a garin Midwestern, yana ganin matakin na iya zama game da karawa Trump damar sake zabarsa.
"Na yi takaici sosai a wannan makon [cewa] shugaban ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci motsi na Black Lives Matter", in ji Lucas, dan Democrat, a kan "Fox News Sunday" na zanga-zangar da aka yi kwanan nan kan rashin daidaiton launin fata da zaluncin 'yan sanda.
"Ba haka lamarin yake a Kansas City ba. Mun samu karuwa a shekara-shekara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kai shi ne a zahiri a share wasu daga cikin kisan da ba a warware ba".
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi kokarin samun takamaiman kuma mai da hankali kan warware kisan... Ina ganin idan kun saurari maganganun kwanan nan... muna farin cikin yin aiki tare da jami'an tarayya a cikin iyakantaccen yanki. "
Duk da shirye-shiryensa na samun jami'an tarayya su yi aiki tare da jami'an tsaro na gida, Lucas ya ce maganganun Trump - musamman a cikin hasken rikice-rikicen da ke tattare da dabarun da jami'an tarayya ke amfani da su a Portland, Oregon - ya sa yawancin masu zaɓe su nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'ai a kan titunan birni.
"Abin da ba mu bukata ba shi ne karin man fetur a kan wuta daga jami'an tarayya don yin, ina tsammanin, batun siyasa mai ban sha'awa", in ji shi.
A ranar Laraba ne Trump ya sanar da cewa zai tura jami'an tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen yaki da karuwar yawan aikata laifuka - wani mataki da ke nuna fadada tsoma bakin fadar White House a cikin tilasta bin doka a yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban "doka da oda".
"Hawan" jami'ai da aka sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da sauran biranen Amurka wani bangare ne na Operation Legend - wanda aka sanya masa suna bayan LeGend Taliferro mai shekaru 4, wanda aka harbe shi yayin da yake bacci a wani gida a Kansas City a ƙarshen watan da ya gabata.
Duk da yake aika jami'an tarayya don taimakawa wajen tabbatar da dokar cikin gida ba sabon abu bane - Babban Lauyan Kasa Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan yunkurin a watan Disamba ga birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - nau'in jami'in tarayya da ake aikawa, da wasu dabarun su, sun tayar da damuwa tsakanin 'yan majalisa na jihohi da na gida.
Da dama daga cikin 'yan majalisar dokokin daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi magana game da gwamnatin Trump da ke tura jami'an zuwa garuruwansu, musamman bayan rahotanni cewa jami'an tarayya da ba a san ko su wanene ba sun kama masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun dauke su a cikin motocin da ba a nuna su ba.
Portland ta sha fama da zanga-zanga kusan kowace rana kan zaluncin 'yan sanda da wariyar launin fata tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd yayin da yake hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
