Kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP ya zargi sakataren manema labarai na fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany saboda "shirye-shiryen siyasa" - amma 'yan jarida suna ci gaba da yin tambayoyi na siyasa - RT USA News
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya zargi sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da ta damu da kafofin yada labarai ta hanyar sanya jawabin ta siyasa maimakon bayani - a bayyane ya manta cewa manema labarai ne ke zabar tambayoyin.
Wani labarin Asabar da AP, babbar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Amurka, ya ce taron manema labarai na fadar White House na iya zama "al'adar da ta lalace", kamar yadda McEnany ya sanya su "wani talla mai kyau, mai cike da talla ga shugaban da ke fuskantar sake zaɓe, wurin da za a kai hari kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin da ke da haske game da bayanai" game da abin da gwamnati ke yi.
Wannan na ƙarshe daga cikin waɗannan maganganun ba shi da hujja, tun da yake ba a bayyana sabon bayani ba a cikin bayanan.
Abin da AP ta kasa ambata shi ne cewa kusan babu wani sabon bayani da ake nema a zahiri a taron.
'Yan jarida sau da yawa suna amfani da masu buga labarai na fadar White House don jawo hankali a kansu, wani nau'in fasaha da Jim Acosta na CNN ya inganta.
Sun wuce alakar adawa da kafofin watsa labarai da kuma gudanarwa, suna maimaita juna wajen yin tambayoyi da suka shafi kawai don kalubalanci Shugaba Donald Trump.
A wasu lokuta, su ne ke sa labarai, kamar lokacin da wakilin CBS News Weijia Jiang ya amsa martani na "tambaya China" daga Trump ta hanyar yin wata alama mai ban mamaki game da wariyar launin fata: "Ya shugaba, me ya sa kake gaya min hakan musamman?"
Wani bayani na ranar 6 ga watan Yuli ya ba da babban misali na rashin haɗin kan yadda bayanan suka daina zama tushen mahimman bayanai ga Amurkawa.
Trump ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa an yi wa tashar talabijin ta NASCAR rauni sakamakon zargin karya na aikata laifin ƙiyayya da direban motar Bubba Wallace da kuma shawarar da ta yanke na hana nuna tutar Confederate a abubuwan da ta ke yi.
Kamar yadda aka zata, yawancin tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet kamar yadda 'yan jarida suka tambayi McEnany tambayoyi da aka tsara don sa ta ce Trump yana goyon bayan tutar Confederate.
McEnany bai ba da amsar da manema labarai ke so ba - murya mai raɗaɗi da za ta cutar da Trump - amma ta maimaita maimaitawa ta hanyar cewa shugaban ba ya ɗaukar matsayi a kan tutar Confederate kuma cewa ainihin saƙonsa shi ne cewa ana nuna magoya bayan NASCAR ba daidai ba ne a matsayin wariyar launin fata.
AP ta ce ta yi sauti "mai haushi" a lokacin taron.
Labarin na AP ya sake maimaita wani shafi na Washington Post a farkon wannan watan daga ɗan jaridar ABC News Jonathan Karl, wanda kuma shi ne shugaban kungiyar masu ba da rahoto na Fadar White House.
Karl ya yi jayayya, "karyata gaskiyar da kuma amfani da gidan fadar White House don dalilai na siyasa ne kawai shine cin zarafin amincewar jama'a. "
Duk da haka hanzarin McEnany da salon fada sun sanya ta ta zama jaruma ga wasu magoya bayan Trump, tun lokacin da ta ba da sanarwar farko a ranar 1 ga Mayu bayan ta karɓi matsayin sakataren manema labarai a watan Afrilu.
Masu buga littattafan sun yi rashin aiki fiye da shekara guda kafin a naɗa ta.
Kamar sauran bangarorin rayuwar siyasa a Washington, dangantakar sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House da kafofin yada labarai ta canza sosai a zamanin Trump.
Wannan canji ya zo ne daga bangarorin biyu kuma ya kasance kafin zuwan McEnany.
Wani gasa na tsohon sakataren yada labarai Sarah Huckabee Sanders ta dan wasan kwaikwayo Michelle Wolf a gidan White House "abinci a watan Afrilu 2018 ya kasance mai ban tsoro har ma da mai gabatar da MSNBC Mika Brzezinski ya kira shi "abin tausayi".
Wakilin gidan White House na AP Jill Colvin ya gaishe McEnany a lokacin da ta fara bayani ta hanyar tambayar, "Za ku yi alkawarin ba za ku taba yin ƙarya ba daga wannan dandalin?"
Wani mai sharhi kan siyasar Fox News Brit Hume, tsohon dan jarida mai shekaru fiye da 50 a aikin jarida wanda ya yi aiki a 1989-1996 a matsayin babban wakilin gidan White House na ABC, ya ce 'yan jarida a yau suna nuna "halayyar tashin hankali" a dakin taro saboda rashin girmamawarsu ga Trump.
Saboda mayar da hankalinsu kan Trump ne, ya ce a wannan makon a shirin Tucker Carlson Tonight na Fox, 'yan jarida suna yin watsi da tattara labarai na siyasa.
"Ba wasa bane kawai", in ji Hume game da manufar da ake so na masu latsawa.
"Ba wai kawai ana ƙoƙari a kunyata wani jami'in gwamnati ba, amma ana son a samu bayanai".
