Manyan kamfanonin talla suna neman rangwamen daga filayen jiragen sama, majalisun gari
Media ta tara jari a farkon wannan shekarar don samar da ƙarin tabbacin kuɗi yayin da annobar ta fara tsoratar da masu talla.
Majiyoyi sun ce kamfanonin suna tattauna hanyoyin da za su daidaita raguwar da suka yi ta hanyar rage hayar wuraren da suke aiki ko kuma ta hanyar cire ko rage garanti na mafi karancin kudaden shiga, wanda yawanci ake gabatar da shi lokacin da aka fara sanya hannu kan yarjejeniya.
Wani tushe ya nuna cewa manyan kamfanonin talla na iya tabbatar da kashi 85 cikin ɗari na kudaden shigar da aka yi hasashen su a cikin haya.
Wasu kwangila suna da sharudda da ke ba su damar rage mafi ƙarancin garanti idan adadin mutane a cikin wani yanki ya ragu da wani kashi, amma ba a bayyana ko wannan yanayin yana cikin kowane kwangila na yanzu tsakanin kamfanonin talla da masu mallakar su ba.
A lokaci guda, kamfanonin suna ba da rangwame mai yawa ga masu talla don su cika wuraren da ke akwai a kan allon talla kuma su ba su mafi yawan darajar kuɗi da zai yiwu.
Allon talla a Sydney CBD da kuma yankunan da ke kewaye da su, waɗanda yawanci suna da tallace-tallace shida suna gwagwarmaya don cika dukkan wuraren da ake da su.
Amma wasu wurare - kamar su allon talla na mita 40 x 10 na kafofin watsa labarai na oOh! a Filin jirgin saman Sydney - an inganta su.
Kafofin watsa labarai sun ki yin sharhi, amma a wani taron Macquarie Australia a watan Mayu, sun nuna sama da dala miliyan 20 a cikin tanadin kuɗin haya.
JC Decaux ya ki yin sharhi.
Filin jirgin sama da kuma sufuri na jama'a su ne tallace-tallace masu riba ga kamfanonin talla.
A cewar Rahoton Kungiyar Watsa Labarai ta 2019 na waje, kudaden shiga daga sufuri - gami da filayen jiragen sama - ya kai dala miliyan 169.4 yayin da kudaden shiga daga kayan ado na titi da na waje na motocin bas da jiragen kasa ya kai dala miliyan 266.5.
Kasuwancin JC Decaux yana da kwangila tare da Filin jirgin saman Sydney, Yarra Trams, Filin jirgin saman Perth da Sydney Buses. oOh! Media yana da allon talla a yankuna kamar Qantas lounges, a waje da filin jirgin saman Sydney, Filin jirgin saman Adelaide, Filin jirgin saman Darwin da cikin tashoshin jirgin kasa a Sydney da Melbourne.
