Mista Pilot - wanda aka kwace shi daga mukaminsa a jam'iyyar da kuma gwamnati - an ba shi 'yanci na wucin gadi daga rashin cancanta ta hanyar Kotun Koli ta Rajasthan, wacce ta yanke hukuncin cewa Kakakin majalisar ba zai iya daukar wani mataki ba har sai an yanke hukunci game da babbar tambayar da ke tattare da kundin tsarin mulki game da ikonsa.
