AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Wani mota ya ratsa cikin taron jama'a kuma an harbe wani mai zanga-zanga a yankin Aurora na Denver yayin zanga-zangar nuna adawa da rashin adalci.
Sashen 'yan sanda na Aurora ya ce a shafin Twitter cewa masu zanga-zanga suna tafiya a kan hanyar Interstate 225 ranar Asabar lokacin da wata mota ta wuce.
'Yan sanda sun ce wani mai zanga-zanga ya harba bindiga, ya buge akalla mutum daya wanda aka kai asibiti cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Hukumomi sun ce an ja motar kuma suna bincike.
Masu zanga-zangar sun kuma fasa tagogin kotun kuma an fara wuta a wani ofishi, in ji 'yan sanda.
An ayyana taron ba bisa ka'ida ba kuma 'yan sanda sun umarci masu zanga-zanga su bar yankin, in ji hukumomi.
An kara tashin hankali a zanga-zangar da aka yi a baya-bayan nan kan rashin adalci na launin fata tun lokacin da aka tura jami'an tarayya don murkushe zanga-zangar a Portland, Oregon.
'Yan sanda sun ayyana tashe-tashen hankula a Seattle ranar Asabar.
Zanga-zangar da ta taso ne sakamakon mutuwar George Floyd a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu, wani baƙar fata a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan wani farar hula ya riƙe shi a ƙasa tare da gwiwa a wuyansa, ya kuma nuna wasu lokuta na mummunan tashin hankali na 'yan sanda.
A Colorado, masu zanga-zanga sun ja hankali kan mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka dakatar da shi yayin da yake tafiya a kan titin Aurora a watan Agusta 2019 bayan da mai kiran 911 ya ba da rahoton cewa yana da shakku.
'Yan sanda suka sa ya sha wahala, kuma 'yan aikin gaggawa suka ba shi milligram 500 na ketamine, wani magani mai kwantar da hankali, don su kwantar masa da hankali.
