Pakistan ta yi kokarin "sanya baya" ga Indiya duk da kokarin da ta yi na ci gaba da alakar abokantaka, in ji Firayim Minista Narendra Modi a yau a cikin girmamawa ga dakarun soji a ranar cika shekaru 21 da yakin Kargil.
A cikin jawabinsa na rediyo na Mann ki Baat, PM Modi ya ce "Pakistan ta yi wannan mummunan aiki tare da munanan tsare-tsare don kwace ƙasar Indiya da kuma karkatar da rikice-rikicen cikin gida da ke gudana".
"Pakistan ta yi ƙarfin hali ta yi ƙoƙarin mamaye ƙasar Indiya da kuma janye hankali daga tashe-tashen hankulan cikin gida", in ji shi.
"A lokacin, Indiya tana kokarin inganta dangantaka da Pakistan. Amma kamar yadda aka ce, yanayin mugunta shine yaƙi da kowa ba tare da dalili ba. Mutanen wannan yanayin suna iya tunanin yin mugunta ne kawai ga waɗanda suke ƙoƙarin yi musu alheri. Wannan shine dalilin da ya sa Pakistan ta doke Indiya duk da ƙoƙarin Indiya na kyakkyawar dangantaka, "in ji shi..
"Kuna iya tunanin, abokan gaba sun yi ta faman hawa a kan tsaunuka yayin da sojojinmu ke yaƙi da su daga ƙasa. Amma babban halinmu da amincin sojojinmu sun yi nasara a kan tsaunuka", in ji shi.
"Saboda ƙarfin hali na dakarunmu, Indiya ta nuna babban ƙarfi a Kargil", in ji PM Modi, yana tuna ziyarar da ya kai yankin.
Ana bikin Kargil Diwas a kowace shekara, don nuna ranar da sojojin Indiya suka sake kwace dukkan wuraren da sojojin Pakistan suka mamaye a Kargil na Ladakh shekaru 21 da suka gabata.
A ranar 26 ga Yuli, 1999, Sojoji sun sanar da nasarar kammala "Operation Vijay".
Yaƙin da ya ɗauki kusan watanni uku a tsaunukan Ladakh ya yi sanadin mutuwar sojoji sama da 500.
Tun da farko a yau, Ministan Tsaro Rajnath Singh, karamin Ministansa Shripad Naik, Shugaban Sojojin Tsaro Janar Bipin Rawat, Shugaban Sojojin Soja Janar M M Naravane, Shugaban Sojojin Soja R K S Bhadauria da Shugaban Sojojin Ruwa Admiral Karambir Singh suma sun yi ta'aziyya a Amar Jawan Jyoti a National War Memorial.
