An yanke wannan shawarar ne bayan da Spain ta yi rikodin sama da sabbin masu cutar Covid-19 900 a kullum na tsawon kwanaki biyu.
Sakataren harkokin wajen ya yarda cewa ba a bar masu yawon bude ido da yawa ba tare da lokaci ba don soke ko canja shirye-shiryensu.
"Na fahimci cewa yana da matukar damuwa ga wadanda ke fuskantar wannan wanda ke cikin Spain ko kuma suna tunanin zuwa amma dole ne mu iya daukar mataki cikin sauri da kuma tsaurara don kare Burtaniya", in ji shi.
"Mun samu irin wannan ci gaba wajen rage cutar da kuma hana cutar sake shiga Birtaniya".
